    "English": "A popular metal alloy with a wide variety of uses. 'Dirty Bronze' has shed its scientific name in favor of the popular term for its color.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pure Ferrite</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pyrite</span>.",
